  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">SG Ghana SME SL</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The most significant expected Project-level outcome is an increase in the availability of longer-term financing to underserved SMEs. IFC also anticipates that the Project has the potential to promote greater market competitiveness through demonstration of the commercial viability of lending to SMEs.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The proposed project entails the provision of a US$50 million senior loan to Societe Generale Ghana (SG Ghana or the Bank) to support the Banks lending to Small and Medium Enterprises (SMEs) in Ghana.</narrative>
  </description>
